- Gusomera umwana udukuru twanditse, kumuririmbira no 
  gukina na we;
- Kwigisha umwana kwirinda ibintu byamuhutaza;
- Kuvugisha umwana neza utigana imvugo igoretse y’abana;
- Gukomeza konsa umwana unamugaburira indyo yuzuye kandi 
  ihagije;
- Gukingiza umwana inkingo zose;
- Gushishikariza umwana kurya ariko utabimuhatiye;
- Kumuha amategeko yoroshye bitewe n’icyo ushaka kumutoza;
- Gushimira umwana ibyiza akoze, kumufasha iyo atiyizeye, ate 
  ubwoba, no kumwereka urukundo buri gihe.
